---
description: Accessibility and interaction rules
globs: ["src/**/*.tsx"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Even for a power-user desktop app, accessibility matters.

Rules:
- interactive controls must have clear labels
- icon-only buttons must have accessible names/tooltips
- keyboard navigation should work for core actions where practical
- focus states should remain visible
- color alone must not be the only signal for critical state
- error messages should be understandable

Do not:
- hide key actions behind hover-only behavior without alternative access
- rely only on color to indicate staged/conflicted/risky states